data.description: 1354 Morningside Dr. is a classic Laguna Beach ocean view home on an oversized street to street lot. This charmer has all the space of a luxury homesite including sit down ocean views from both levels. Located in Bluebird Canyon it's private and protected from the hustle and bustle however just minutes to downtown Laguna's most beautiful beaches, restaurants & shopping. Home of famed Laguna Beach artist and sculptor Patricia Turnier you can see where much of her inspiration came from. Surrounded by beauty, the property is nestled in a tranquil setting surrounded by trees with views from every window and deck. Now it's time for a new owner with vision and appreciation of the Laguna lifestyle to enjoy this opportunity. Oh, and also what to do with all this land?!  Large lots like this  don't come on the market often so it is expected this will move quickly. Location, location, location is truly where the value lies and with endless opportunities for the new owner to make it their own.  Downstairs there is a non-conforming wholly contained studio. This peaceful space includes full kitchen & bath, living/sleeping space with cozy fireplace. Multiple windows surround this sanctuary with view decks surrounded by lush greenery.  Don't miss an opportunity to create your family masterpiece here in the beautiful hills of Bluebird Canyon.
